This paper deals with large-scale machine learning problems, specifically using parallel algorithms for model parallel blockwise updates. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of asynchronous communication between worker nodes and parameter servers, which is a common topic in Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions the use of large amounts of training data, which is a topic in Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the convergence behavior and speedup of the proposed algorithm, which is a topic in Systems and Control (cs.SY).
